      "image_alt": "Aerial view of Oravec Isle in Nifty Island showing a small sandy island with palm trees, collectible Blooms, and a character standing at the center",
      "layer": "status",
      "type": "article",
      "body_html": "<figure><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/stephenoravec-media/blog/2026/04/25/oravec-isle-overview-1000.webp\" srcset=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/stephenoravec-media/blog/2026/04/25/oravec-isle-overview-400.webp 400w, https://storage.googleapis.com/stephenoravec-media/blog/2026/04/25/oravec-isle-overview-1000.webp 1000w, https://storage.googleapis.com/stephenoravec-media/blog/2026/04/25/oravec-isle-overview-2000.webp 2000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 1000px\" alt=\"Overview of kidney-shaped Oravec Isle from above showing palm trees, blooms, the island campfire, and a character bouncing on a trampoline\" loading=\"lazy\"></figure>\n<p>This kidney-shaped little island has it all: white sand, palm trees, a campfire, trampoline, and 10 Blooms for visitors to collect.</p>\n<figure><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/stephenoravec-media/blog/2026/04/25/oravec-isle-shore-1000.webp\" srcset=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/stephenoravec-media/blog/2026/04/25/oravec-isle-shore-400.webp 400w, https://storage.googleapis.com/stephenoravec-media/blog/2026/04/25/oravec-isle-shore-1000.webp 1000w, https://storage.googleapis.com/stephenoravec-media/blog/2026/04/25/oravec-isle-shore-2000.webp 2000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 1000px\" alt=\"View from the water looking at Oravec Isle shore with glowing Bloom collectibles lined across the beach and a character wading in the shallow water\" loading=\"lazy\"></figure>\n<p>Don't hesitate to wade out into the water. This metaverse experience is shark, sea serpent, and mine free.</p>\n<figure><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/stephenoravec-media/blog/2026/04/25/oravec-isle-point-1000.webp\" srcset=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/stephenoravec-media/blog/2026/04/25/oravec-isle-point-400.webp 400w, https://storage.googleapis.com/stephenoravec-media/blog/2026/04/25/oravec-isle-point-1000.webp 1000w, https://storage.googleapis.com/stephenoravec-media/blog/2026/04/25/oravec-isle-point-2000.webp 2000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 1000px\" alt=\"Top-down view of one end of Oravec Isle with a character collecting Bloom collectibles on the sand by running through them\" loading=\"lazy\"></figure>\n<p>Blooms line the shoreline. A short jog around the island will net you ten.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://niftyis.land/stephenoravec/isle\">Visit Oravec Isle on Nifty Island today!</a></p>",
